data.description: This is the home you have been waiting for, nestled in the sought out community of Wigwam Creek. Between the fully remodeled chef's kitchen and the entertainers backyard, you simply can't go wrong. This beautiful 3 bed, 2 bath home has so much to offer; family room with wood beams, living room, remodeled laundry room, big kitchen island, RO system, gas range, wine fridge, firepit/seating area out back & water fall at the pool. The master bath has beautiful travertine tile and dual sinks. This home has been loved and well taken care of. It is now ready for the next owner to show it the same love and care all the while putting your own stamp on it.
